function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

--idOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

--Spirit speaking. 
Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation("QST_DSQ_LadyOasis_01", idActor)

Hydra.Wait(5.0)

tGhosts = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_DSQ_LadyOasis_Ghosts_ActorGroup")

for i, Spawners in ipairs(tGhosts) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Spawners) then
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(Spawners)
			--Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(Spawners, false) 
		end
	end

end
